Jupyter Notebook','https://github.com/HandsOnLLM/Hands-On-Large-Language-Models','handsonllm-hands-on-large-language-models','HandsOnLLM/Hands-On-Large-Language-Models - GitHub Trending AI Project','Official code repo for the O\'Reilly Book - \"Hands-On Large Language Models\"','[\"llm\", \"jupyter notebook\", \"github\", \"trending\", \"open-source\"]','2026-06-10 06:08:20.768'),(11,'yamadashy/repomix','📦 Repomix is a powerful tool that packs your entire repository into a single, AI-friendly file. Perfect for when you need to feed your codebase to Large Language Models (LLMs) or other AI tools like Claude, ChatGPT, DeepSeek, Perplexity, Gemini, Gemma, Llama, Grok, and more.',26133,392,'mcp','TypeScript','https://github.com/yamadashy/repomix','yamadashy-repomix','yamadashy/repomix - GitHub Trending AI Project','📦 Repomix is a powerful tool that packs your entire repository into a single, AI-friendly file. Perfect for when you need to feed your codebase to Large Langua','[\"mcp\", \"typescript\", \"github\", \"trending\", \"open-source\"]','2026-06-10 06:08:21.449'),(12,'PrefectHQ/fastmcp','🚀 The fast, Pythonic way to build MCP servers and clients.',25566,397,'agents','Python','https://github.com/PrefectHQ/fastmcp','prefecthq-fastmcp','PrefectHQ/fastmcp - GitHub Trending AI Project','🚀 The fast, Pythonic way to build MCP servers and clients.','[\"agents\", \"python\", \"github\", \"trending\", \"open-source\"]','2026-06-10 06:08:22.130'),(13,'deepset-ai/haystack','Open-source AI orchestration framework for building context-engineered, production-ready LLM applications. Design modular pipelines and agent workflows with explicit control over retrieval, routing, memory, and generation. Built for scalable agents, RAG, multimodal applications, semantic search, and conversational systems.',25507,304,'agents','MDX','https://github.com/deepset-ai/haystack','deepset-ai-haystack','deepset-ai/haystack - GitHub Trending AI Project','Open-source AI orchestration framework for building context-engineered, production-ready LLM applications. Design modular pipelines and agent workflows with exp','[\"agents\", \"mdx\", \"github\", \"trending\", \"open-source\"]','2026-06-10 06:08:22.812'),(14,'zai-org/Open-AutoGLM','An Open Phone Agent Model & Framework. Unlocking the AI Phone for Everyone',25477,204,'agents','Python','https://github.com/zai-org/Open-AutoGLM','zai-org-open-autoglm','zai-org/Open-AutoGLM - GitHub Trending AI Project','An Open Phone Agent Model & Framework. Unlocking the AI Phone for Everyone','[\"agents\", \"python\", \"github\", \"trending\", \"open-source\"]','2026-06-10 06:08:23.494'),(15,'p-e-w/heretic','Fully automatic censorship removal for language models',24071,206,'llm','Python','https://github.com/p-e-w/heretic','p-e-w-heretic','p-e-w/heretic - GitHub Trending AI Project','Fully automatic censorship removal for language models','[\"llm\", \"python\", \"github\", \"trending\", \"open-source\"]','2026-06-10 06:08:24.178'),(16,'activepieces/activepieces','AI Agents & MCPs & AI Workflow Automation • (~400 MCP servers for AI agents) • AI Automation / AI Agent with MCPs • AI Workflows & AI Agents • MCPs for AI Agents',22676,224,'agents','TypeScript','https://github.com/activepieces/activepieces','activepieces-activepieces','activepieces/activepieces - GitHub Trending AI Project','AI Agents & MCPs & AI Workflow Automation • (~400 MCP servers for AI agents) • AI Automation / AI Agent with MCPs • AI Workflows & AI Agents • MCPs for AI Agent','[\"agents\", \"typescript\", \"github\", \"trending\", \"open-source\"]','2026-06-10 06:08:24.859'),(17,'QwenLM/Qwen','The official repo of Qwen (通义千问) chat & pretrained large language model proposed by Alibaba Cloud.',21266,136,'llm','Python','https://github.com/QwenLM/Qwen','qwenlm-qwen','QwenLM/Qwen - GitHub Trending AI Project','The official repo of Qwen (通义千问) chat & pretrained large language model proposed by Alibaba Cloud.','[\"llm\", \"python\", \"github\", \"trending\", \"open-source\"]','2026-06-10 06:08:25.545'),(18,'chopratejas/headroom','Compress tool outputs, logs, files, and RAG chunks before they reach the LLM. 60-95% fewer tokens, same answers. Library, proxy, MCP server.',20890,360,'agents','Python','https://github.com/chopratejas/headroom','chopratejas-headroom','chopratejas/headroom - GitHub Trending AI Project','Compress tool outputs, logs, files, and RAG chunks before they reach the LLM. 60-95% fewer tokens, same answers. Library, proxy, MCP server.','[\"agents\", \"python\", \"github\", \"trending\", \"open-source\"]','2026-06-10 06:08:26.229'),(19,'elizaOS/eliza','Open source agentic operating system',18546,183,'agents','TypeScript','https://github.com/elizaOS/eliza','elizaos-eliza','elizaOS/eliza - GitHub Trending AI Project','Open source agentic operating system','[\"agents\", \"typescript\", \"github\", \"trending\", \"open-source\"]','2026-06-10 06:08:26.918'),(20,'agent0ai/agent-zero','Agent Zero AI framework',17999,326,'agents','Python','https://github.com/agent0ai/agent-zero','agent0ai-agent-zero','agent0ai/agent-zero - GitHub Trending AI Project','Agent Zero AI framework','[\"agents\", \"python\", \"github\", \"trending\", \"open-source\"]','2026-06-10 06:08:27.603'),(21,'camel-ai/camel','🐫 CAMEL: The first and the best multi-agent framework. Finding the Scaling Law of Agents. https://www.camel-ai.org',17154,237,'agents','Python','https://github.com/camel-ai/camel','camel-ai-camel','camel-ai/camel - GitHub Trending AI Project','🐫 CAMEL: The first and the best multi-agent framework. Finding the Scaling Law of Agents. https://www.camel-ai.org','[\"agents\", \"python\", \"github\", \"trending\", \"open-source\"]','2026-06-10 06:08:28.290'),(22,'googleapis/mcp-toolbox','MCP Toolbox for Databases is an open source MCP server for databases.',15545,512,'agents','Go','https://github.com/googleapis/mcp-toolbox','googleapis-mcp-toolbox','googleapis/mcp-toolbox - GitHub Trending AI Project','MCP Toolbox for Databases is an open source MCP server for databases.','[\"agents\", \"go\", \"github\", \"trending\", \"open-source\"]','2026-06-10 06:08:28.977'),(23,'GLips/Figma-Context-MCP','MCP server to provide Figma layout information to AI coding agents like Cursor',15048,232,'agents','TypeScript','https://github.com/GLips/Figma-Context-MCP','glips-figma-context-mcp','GLips/Figma-Context-MCP - GitHub Trending AI Project','MCP server to provide Figma layout information to AI coding agents like Cursor','[\"agents\", \"typescript\", \"github\", \"trending\", \"open-source\"]','2026-06-10 06:08:29.657'),(24,'Unstructured-IO/unstructured','Convert documents to structured data effortlessly. Unstructured is open-source ETL solution for transforming complex documents into clean, structured formats for language models.  Visit our website to learn more about our enterprise grade Platform product for production grade workflows, partitioning, enrichments, chunking and embedding.',14874,528,'rag','HTML','https://github.com/Unstructured-IO/unstructured','unstructured-io-unstructured','Unstructured-IO/unstructured - GitHub Trending AI Project','Convert documents to structured data effortlessly. Unstructured is open-source ETL solution for transforming complex documents into clean, structured formats fo','[\"rag\", \"html\", \"github\", \"trending\", \"open-source\"]','2026-06-10 06:08:30.477'),(25,'owainlewis/awesome-artificial-intelligence','A curated list of Artificial Intelligence (AI) courses, books, video lectures and papers.',14045,514,'tools','Unknown','https://github.com/owainlewis/awesome-artificial-intelligence','owainlewis-awesome-artificial-intelligence','owainlewis/awesome-artificial-intelligence - GitHub Trending AI Project','A curated list of Artificial Intelligence (AI) courses, books, video lectures and papers.','[\"tools\", \"unknown\", \"github\", \"trending\", \"open-source\"]','2026-06-10 06:08:31.162');
